<blockquote class="gmail_quote" style="margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex">If I&#39;m not wrong, you just have to link the right libraries and be sure the preprocessor will find the header files. Usually, the mpicc is a compiler wraper that does that for you. Check if actually it is not a script that you can just change the content to adapt it to your necessities.<br>


